Package au.edu.anu.omhtk.rng

package au.edu.anu.omhtk.rng

Implements various peudo-random number generators.

Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 18 mai 2021
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Pcg32
    Implementation of a permuted congruential generator (PCG).
    RandomSeeds
    A static list of 1,000 true random integer numbers generated from "atmospheric noise" on 10/07/2018 found here, to use as seeds for pseudo-random number generators.
    XSRandom
    Implementation of George Marsaglia's elegant Xorshift random generator (2003), 30% faster and better quality than the built-in Random.
